{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a1882d2439","title":"大字报一束","origin":"《四川省右派言论选辑5》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月30日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"095daaeb0c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"a1882d2439"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"222c241b8a","name":"成都工学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7c1dc3e1a6","type":"title","text":"大字报一束","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"874032bf11","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"31408233bc","type":"paragraph","text":"建议：1．取消党委制，建立校委制(废除党委制度，不是争鸣党委的领导)。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"b0b8a5e097","type":"paragraph","text":"2．立即取消辅导员制，由老师负责培养同学。辅导员既不懂业务，又未教政治课，怎样来辅导同学？大学生不是小妹妹，连一点政治素养都没有吗？不是来监视同学言行自由是做什么？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"412de051df","type":"paragraph","text":"3．支持所有鸣者要求，取消三角制，建立班委制。班干部应由同学民主选举，不应是青一色的党团员。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"879ba03643","type":"paragraph","text":"班三角还有民主吗？","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"e9fbdc35eb","type":"paragraph","text":"班三角，不民主，谁领导、党小组，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"e46c7bc1d2","type":"paragraph","text":"班长由院长任命，代表行政总揽班上大权。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"f48720fc96","type":"paragraph","text":"团支书只代表班上团员，但一切都得由他指点。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"f86c9def3a","type":"paragraph","text":"学生代表是同学选，但只把文娱活动来管。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"903131b8e9","type":"paragraph","text":"选举权吧，同学们只有一遍。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"5ca8872979","type":"paragraph","text":"团员选了学生代表还有支书的特权。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"ce1f719527","type":"paragraph","text":"党员更不用说，在级上有他的领导权。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"b3c2d06ffa","type":"paragraph","text":"学校、系上有要事都把班长来喊，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"3d1c4bdcb5","type":"paragraph","text":"另外还有党团组织干部参加提意见。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"5e97655f78","type":"paragraph","text":"学生代表有职无权却丢在一遍。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"b75e599fd6","type":"paragraph","text":"班三角，官僚机构干部成团，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"478198f8c4","type":"paragraph","text":"有干事有组长，还有板报编辑人员。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"94ef0c0f2c","type":"paragraph","text":"开会时党小组领导，支委参加占人数一半，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"18ad8561e5","type":"paragraph","text":"官多兵少，事难办，丢下摊子无人管。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"1f4eaab553","type":"paragraph","text":"班三角之优越性，不知如何体现？","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"35a584de86","type":"paragraph","text":"这是生硬照苏联把教条来搬。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"7e87cb143f","type":"paragraph","text":"建议立即取消，采班委由同学来选，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"07774520b9","type":"paragraph","text":"既民主，工作又好办。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"9823da7e01","type":"paragraph","text":"坚决反对学生会、广播台、班三角的大官人员，一律用傀儡无能的党团员充任。我们认为不参加共产党、共青团还是同样能为人类造福。全体非党团员的同学们，工人们，教职工们，我们以“五四”先烈的精神来争取人权自由、政治平等，不准谁来追踪、调查、了解我们。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"2ecd82f4d0","type":"paragraph","text":"基督教徒一手划十字，适(还？)考政治，真主在上！考完试我再忏悔吧！我本来不信……但这是制度啊！饶恕我吧！","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"500658f0cd","type":"paragraph","text":"抗议：学校行政久久不答覆政治课考试问题，希望校方明智，以免“造成大民主”！","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"b7f56f9caa","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要求听太平洋彼岸美国先进的科学报告！毛主席说要打败敌人就要学敌人的优点。美国的工程技术科学已经创造了很多奇迹，很多方面在世界上首屈一指。我们反对把我们培养成偏见，鼻闻心目中只有苏联的教育制度，我们同美国的劳动者永远心连心的在一起。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"299fe965bc","type":"paragraph","text":"我们反对：1．俄文必修。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"5e7616b22d","type":"paragraph","text":"2．硬搬苏联的教材教育制度(如五分制)。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"240542bc81","type":"paragraph","text":"3．支部书记领导全班同学群众。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"ab95a70fb7","type":"paragraph","text":"4．辅导员制度。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"512610bc7b","type":"paragraph","text":"5．班长指定。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"d25ed64967","type":"paragraph","text":"6．学生会是傀儡。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"9bbb3e4579","type":"paragraph","text":"解决办法：","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"3119b6761b","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)下期立即开设遍及全球的世界语——英文。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"89168de63d","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)建议用我们自己编写的讲义教材，没有的或苏联好的部分保存下来，实行学分制。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"dfeaabfcde","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)支书只管团支部，没资格领导同学，若硬要领导就是党派主义！","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"d5eab4227d","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)辅导员文化低，政治修养差，东走西站似乎在奔忙，其实只接触几个党团员上层干部，偏听偏信害人不浅！立即取缔机械系不学无术的政治辅导员，建议她转业！","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"c286f8e91b","type":"paragraph","text":"(5)班长民主选。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"},{"id":"9adb3a0d8e","type":"paragraph","text":"(6)学生会由全校民主选，个人亦可参加竞选。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439"}],"page":{"id":"fd8fade60b","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1882d2439","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}